    <detaileddescription>
<para>This is an internal object of the <ref refid="classStatistiques" kindref="compound">Statistiques</ref> class that encapsulate informations about counters. For each numerical simulation, a unique Stat_Internals is created at the start of the computation and associated with the <ref refid="classStatistiques" kindref="compound">Statistiques</ref> type object. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
